name: VORTEX EYES #01
description: Artist: Betty Mü, Video Loop, 1210x1200 Pixels, 00:56 Minutes, Original Creation Date: 01. June 2019,  By showing cyclical forms that are constantly changing, Betty Mü’s surreal videomapping installation draws the viewer’s gaze into the vortex of a hypnotic time warp. A vast current of stimuli forces the viewer into a dialogue in order to decipher the story that is circling around. The VORTEX series started 2016.
